---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Terms of Use" description="PlainHazard terms of use. Conditions for using our natural disaster and weather data portal.">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">Last updated: March 2026</p>
    <div class="mt-8 space-y-6 text-sm leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Acceptance</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">By using PlainHazard, you agree to these terms. If you disagree, please discontinue use.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Data Accuracy</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">PlainHazard presents data from FEMA disaster declarations and NOAA Storm Events Database. While we strive for accuracy, we make no warranty that data is complete, current, or error-free. Data is provided "as is" for informational purposes only.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Not Professional Advice</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">PlainHazard is not an emergency management agency. Content does not constitute safety, insurance, or risk assessment advice. Consult local emergency management for specific guidance.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Intellectual Property</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">The underlying data is public domain (U.S. government work). Our presentation, design, and analysis are copyrighted. You may not scrape, reproduce, or redistribute our pages without permission.</p>
      </section>
      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white">Contact</h2>
        <p class="mt-2">Questions? Contact <a href="mailto:legal@plainhazard.com" class="text-brand-600 hover:underline dark:text-brand-400">legal@plainhazard.com</a>.</p>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
